uote":{"pid":"07cebb7a2d1c8c39eb8cd6e93b2c7d1810e2aa41","tid":1384801,"uid":81195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:58:59.000Z","msg":"頭先出門口嗰陣，撞到個隔離屋藍絲阿叔，打完一輪招呼廢話之後就講<br />\n🐝：藍絲<br />\n🐜：我<br />\n<br />\n🐝： 又有班冷坦今朝搞地鐵啦！ 搞到我都做咗要出門口！<br />\n<br />\n當時嘅我真係想放棄一切，狠狠地打鳩佢一鑊，但我冇咁做，我決定嘗試盡我嘅說話令佢明白。<br />\n<br />\n🐜：不如你換個角度睇，先唔好理件事係啱定錯，而家200萬人出黎<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">伸冤</span></span>，但個政府都可以唔理！你諗下，如果有一日要伸冤嘅嗰個係你，你個冤要有幾大先可以令政府理？<br />\n<br />\n佢聽到<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">伸冤</span></span>之後兩個字！<br />\n我feel到！<br />\n我真係feel到！<br />\n佢個腦開始運作返！<br />\n我feel到佢喺度ff緊自己有冤伸會點！！<br />\n<br />\n佢地 係睇古裝片大！<br />\n佢唔明白乜嘢係示威 ！<br />\n但係佢好明白乜嘢係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">伸冤</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:20:24.000Z","msg":"Well done."},{"pid":"50d9c43dfbd00e56f5589784ad754c442a4c6aae","tid":1384801,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:22:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我屌又真係諗唔到呢個字眼"},{"pid":"54a2e2964d49e31e9b4e9cac70464b6fe6a4eda1","tid":1384801,"uid":198309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:22:30.000Z","msg":"我屋企條垃圾廢老連有100萬200萬人都唔撚信 on9"},{"pid":"8ed597f1ffad3b7030dceafd8b848c615501b8e2","tid":1384801,"uid":81195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54a2e2964d49e31e9b4e9cac70464b6fe6a4eda1","tid":1384801,"uid":198309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:22:30.000Z","msg":"我屋企條垃圾廢老連有100萬200萬人都唔撚信 on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:27:40.000Z","msg":"試下今日返去同佢講係<span style=\"color: red;\">伸冤<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span></span>"},{"pid":"c5fe63145dcd34e819678e695964c639113627a7","tid":1384801,"uid":81195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50d9c43dfbd00e56f5589784ad754c442a4c6aae","tid":1384801,"uid":89974,"like":0,"di