賊<br />\n7) 冧市第時後生好似大陸咁月薪5千 點養你<br />\n<br />\n對上班族<br />\n1) 白領: 香港變到深圳咁 請人點解請香港人貪貴?<br />\n2) 藍領: 將來反送中(及一干國策)通過, 香港冧市 情況仲慘過當年沙士通縮 一個月無一次工返既日子<br />\n3)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:44:24.000Z","msg":"神作"},{"pid":"136a32d215ff04e6438d4164275bc181ab31c8b5","tid":1384801,"uid":81195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:48:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而家係朝廷派兵打伸冤嘅人啊</span></span>"},{"pid":"c4eeb8147b9c05c738925d8f4ba3edc2668b0871","tid":1384801,"uid":56512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:48:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6a1061fb7210bbe18369e46168bdfe01aa59d41a","tid":1384801,"uid":81195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4eeb8147b9c05c738925d8f4ba3edc2668b0871","tid":1384801,"uid":56512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:48:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:53:52.000Z","msg":"多謝幫推！"},{"pid":"6e3a44f9e50ba17ed54fa86d3c84ba3da657606d","tid":1384801,"uid":81195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:01:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c6a741bb96a9c86e993880ab14b2462038d1ade","tid":1384801,"uid":81195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:22:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4ec252e753dbb3f4fce59e505c928a083d9f97","tid":1384801,"uid":23738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:29:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2704b684b81adfbd29fa00a1565c4c31e9e5f71b","tid":1384801,"uid":262784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:34:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大人伸